<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Tools on Gyeongmin Lee</title><link>https://gyeongmin.kr/en/categories/tools/</link><description>Recent content in Tools on Gyeongmin Lee</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><copyright>Gyeongmin Lee</copyright><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Jan 2023 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/categories/tools/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Baekjoon Discord Bot 'BaekjoonBot'</title><link>https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/</link><pubDate>Tue, 03 Jan 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-1.png" alt="Featured image of post Baekjoon Discord Bot 'BaekjoonBot'" />&lt;h1 id="baekjoon-discord-bot-baekjoonbot">Baekjoon Discord Bot &amp;lsquo;BaekjoonBot&amp;rsquo;&lt;/h1>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>I built this to post Baekjoon problems in a cleaner format during study sessions.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-1.png"
width="1187"
height="904"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-1_hu3ba0e11ccd78cd419cf9cf4dfafe4b05_113858_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-1_hu3ba0e11ccd78cd419cf9cf4dfafe4b05_113858_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="131"
data-flex-basis="315px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>Built using the &lt;a class="link" href="https://solvedac.github.io/unofficial-documentation/#/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>solved.ac Unofficial API&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-2.png"
width="1500"
height="500"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-2_hua3f398f3dc87c7c8d5a4fd5322b217a0_123732_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-2_hua3f398f3dc87c7c8d5a4fd5322b217a0_123732_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="300"
data-flex-basis="720px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="how-to-use">How to Use&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="post-a-problem">Post a problem&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>You can post a problem with &lt;code>/백준 문제번호&lt;/code>.
&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-6.png"
width="962"
height="81"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-6_hu2facb2ba88d2dbba0ca32a6b9c440ab0_3694_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-6_hu2facb2ba88d2dbba0ca32a6b9c440ab0_3694_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="1187"
data-flex-basis="2850px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Or post with &lt;code>/백준 문제링크&lt;/code>.
&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-7.png"
width="1121"
height="97"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-7_hu0f6723ab47112f2b9c890bf47ad2c7cd_7752_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-7_hu0f6723ab47112f2b9c890bf47ad2c7cd_7752_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="1155"
data-flex-basis="2773px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="post-a-problem-with-source-code">Post a problem with source code&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>If you enter source code below &lt;code>/백준 문제번호&lt;/code> or &lt;code>/백준 문제링크&lt;/code>, you can post the problem together with your code.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Use &lt;code>Shift&lt;/code> + &lt;code>Enter&lt;/code> for line breaks.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-4.png"
width="964"
height="517"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-4_hu95272da1a80a9eb9e31f98224bb7d4be_32035_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-4_hu95272da1a80a9eb9e31f98224bb7d4be_32035_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="186"
data-flex-basis="447px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>As shown above, using Discord code blocks lets you upload syntax-highlighted code.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-3.png"
width="970"
height="587"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-3_hu42b54d877be7b417125bc335b2754ff6_54257_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-3_hu42b54d877be7b417125bc335b2754ff6_54257_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="165"
data-flex-basis="396px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="when-the-source-code-is-long">When the source code is long&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Discord embeds have a 4,096-character limit.&lt;br>
If the content exceeds the embed limit, it will be displayed as shown below.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-8.png"
width="959"
height="590"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-8_hu2df989813509d31de0633370673ec202_51433_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-8_hu2df989813509d31de0633370673ec202_51433_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="162"
data-flex-basis="390px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>If the command is invalid, it prints “잘못된 입력입니다.” (“Invalid input.”).&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-5.png"
width="959"
height="590"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-5_hu2df989813509d31de0633370673ec202_51433_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-5_hu2df989813509d31de0633370673ec202_51433_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="162"
data-flex-basis="390px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>If sending the embed fails, or if the solved.ac server is unstable and data cannot be retrieved, it prints “메세지 전송이 실패했습니다.” (“Failed to send message.”).&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-9.png"
width="960"
height="69"
srcset="https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-9_hu48de6d47a3ff341ae85709b5d734bb5b_10853_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongmin.kr/en/p/baekjoonbot/image-9_hu48de6d47a3ff341ae85709b5d734bb5b_10853_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="1391"
data-flex-basis="3339px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
